1
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:03,880
<Default><b>[♪ Dramatic
orchestral music]</b></Default>

2
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:14,750
<Default><b>{\i1}My name is
Naofumi Iwatani.{\i0}</b></Default>

3
00:00:15,419 --> 00:00:17,396
<Default><b>{\i1}Before I was summoned{\i0}
{\i1}into this world</b></Default>

4
00:00:17,420 --> 00:00:19,670
<Default><b>{\i1}I was like any other{\i0}
{\i1}college student.{\i0}</b></Default>

5
00:00:19,750 --> 00:00:22,350
<Default><b>{\i1}But here I am, one{\i0}
{\i1}of the four Cardinal heroes.{\i0}</b></Default>

6
00:00:22,420 --> 00:00:23,820
<Default><b>{\i1}The Shield Hero.{\i0}</b></Default>

7
00:00:24,289 --> 00:00:26,609
<Default><b>{\i1}The four heroes have never{\i0}
{\i1}gotten along.{\i0}</b></Default>

8
00:00:26,670 --> 00:00:29,510
<Default><b>{\i1}But as of late, it seems like{\i0}
{\i1}that might be changing.{\i0}</b></Default>

9
00:00:29,789 --> 00:00:31,989
<Default><b>{\i1}Not that we can{\i0}
{\i1}take advantage of it.{\i0}</b></Default>

10
00:00:32,039 --> 00:00:34,515
<Default><b>{\i1}Because just when things{\i0}
{\i1}were looking up for once</b></Default>

11
00:00:34,539 --> 00:00:37,170
<Default><b>{\i1}Raphtalia's
parents' homeland</b></Default>

12
00:00:37,250 --> 00:00:39,329
<Default><b>{\i1}sent assassins
into my lands.{\i0}</b></Default>

13
00:00:40,039 --> 00:00:41,759
<Default><b>{\i1}It all happened so fast.{\i0}</b></Default>

14
00:00:41,829 --> 00:00:44,015
<Default><b>{\i1}The second Raphtalia{\i0}
{\i1}put on the miko outfit{\i0}</b></Default>

15
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:46,515
<Default><b>{\i1}that resembled the clothes{\i0}
{\i1}worn by their emperor</b></Default>

16
00:00:46,539 --> 00:00:47,859
<Default><b>{\i1}they attacked.{\i0}</b></Default>

17
00:00:49,250 --> 00:00:52,130
<Default><b>[♪ Dramatic,
triumphant music]</b></Default>

18
00:00:55,170 --> 00:00:57,936
<Default><b>{\i1}Now I'm on my way to Siltvelt{\i0}
{\i1}to try and catch a ship{\i0}</b></Default>

19
00:00:57,960 --> 00:01:00,515
<Default><b>{\i1}to Q'ten Lo, where hopefully{\i0}
{\i1}I can talk some sense{\i0}</b></Default>

20
00:01:00,539 --> 00:01:03,299
<Default><b>{\i1}into these fools and get{\i0}
{\i1}to the bottom of all this.{\i0}</b></Default>

21
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,420
<Default><b>{\i1}On top of all that</b></Default>

22
00:01:09,209 --> 00:01:10,646
<Default><b>{\i1}But before it does</b></Default>

23
00:01:10,670 --> 00:01:13,390
<Default><b>{\i1}I need to deal with Q'ten Lo{\i0}
{\i1}for Raphtalia's sake.{\i0}</b></Default>

24
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:15,300
<Default><b>{\i1}Her future
depends on it.{\i0}</b></Default>

25
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:17,079
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

26
00:01:17,670 --> 00:01:18,710
<Default><b>[growl]</b></Default>

27
00:01:20,170 --> 00:01:21,570
<Default><b>Yeah. All right.</b></Default>

28
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,959
<Default><b>I think it's time
we take a break.</b></Default>

29
00:01:28,459 --> 00:01:30,920
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

30
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,080
<Default><b>[growl]</b></Default>

31
00:01:39,170 --> 00:01:41,879
<Default><b>Thanks for
checking on me</b></Default>

32
00:01:42,170 --> 00:01:43,250
<Default><b>[sneeze]</b></Default>

33
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:46,935
<Default><b>Seeing as we'll be approaching
the border soon</b></Default>

34
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:49,016
<Default><b>it's probably best
I head back to my land</b></Default>

35
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,680
<Default><b>and regroup my forces.</b></Default>

36
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:51,790
<Default><b>[growl]</b></Default>

37
00:01:52,129 --> 00:01:53,209
<Default><b>Gaelion?</b></Default>

38
00:01:53,290 --> 00:01:54,490
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

39
00:01:55,209 --> 00:01:57,170
<Default><b>¡Drifa Aqua Blast!</b></Default>

40
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,790
<Default><b>[water rushing]</b></Default>

41
00:01:59,329 --> 00:02:00,449
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

42
00:02:03,329 --> 00:02:04,369
<Default><b>[growl]</b></Default>

43
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:08,220
<Default><b>Did you miss me, Master?</b></Default>

44
00:02:08,289 --> 00:02:09,329
<Default><b>¡Raphy!</b></Default>

45
00:02:09,379 --> 00:02:09,919
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

46
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,960
<Default><b>What the hell?</b></Default>

47
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,056
<Default><b>Why are you here?</b></Default>

48
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,879
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

49
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,240
<Default><b>At least pretend
to be happy to see us.</b></Default>

50
00:02:15,289 --> 00:02:17,265
<Default><b>How did you
expect me to react?</b></Default>

51
00:02:17,289 --> 00:02:19,976
<Default><b>You three are supposed to be
off training right now.</b></Default>

52
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,515
<Default><b>Why, yes, and that's exactly
what we were doing.</b></Default>

53
00:02:22,539 --> 00:02:24,855
<Default><b>So you're telling me
it was just a coincidence</b></Default>

54
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:26,265
<Default><b>that you ran
into me here?</b></Default>

55
00:02:26,289 --> 00:02:27,539
<Default><b>Well, um.</b></Default>

56
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:29,169
<Default><b>So you see</b></Default>

57
00:02:29,250 --> 00:02:30,806
<Default><b>we were busy training</b></Default>

58
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:32,390
<Default><b>when we met Fitoria.</b></Default>

59
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:33,765
<Default><b>Wait. Fitoria?</b></Default>

60
00:02:33,789 --> 00:02:35,556
<Default><b>She told us
if we headed this way</b></Default>

61
00:02:35,580 --> 00:02:37,556
<Default><b>that we would eventually
run into you.</b></Default>

62
00:02:37,580 --> 00:02:39,765
<Default><b>She also mentioned
she had a request for us</b></Default>

63
00:02:39,789 --> 00:02:41,556
<Default><b>she wanted me
to tell you about.</b></Default>

64
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:42,645
<Default><b>Tell me later.</b></Default>

65
00:02:42,669 --> 00:02:44,515
<Default><b>I've got my hands full
at the moment</b></Default>

66
00:02:44,539 --> 00:02:47,056
<Default><b>dealing with something
that can't be ignored.</b></Default>

67
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,080
<Default><b>Raphy?</b></Default>

68
00:02:48,330 --> 00:02:48,919
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

69
00:02:49,169 --> 00:02:50,806
<Default><b>Can't you at
least hear her out?</b></Default>

70
00:02:50,830 --> 00:02:52,855
<Default><b>Not only did she already pay
in advance</b></Default>

71
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,895
<Default><b>but she also did
a lot to help us.</b></Default>

72
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:55,976
<Default><b>Oh, really?</b></Default>

73
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,015
<Default><b>And how exactly
did she do that?</b></Default>

74
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,105
<Default><b>Just look.</b></Default>

75
00:02:59,129 --> 00:03:02,015
<Default><b>In exchange for lowering
our levels a bit here and there</b></Default>

76
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:04,080
<Default><b>she gave our
stats a huge boost.</b></Default>

77
00:03:05,419 --> 00:03:06,899
<Default><b>{\i1}She isn't kidding.{\i0}</b></Default>

78
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,105
<Default><b>{\i1}From the looks of it</b></Default>

79
00:03:08,129 --> 00:03:10,529
<Default><b>{\i1}all of their stats{\i0}
{\i1}have more than doubled.{\i0}</b></Default>

80
00:03:11,419 --> 00:03:12,899
<Default><b>It doesn't matter.</b></Default>

81
00:03:16,210 --> 00:03:17,976
<Default><b>Will you hold
on a second?</b></Default>

82
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,560
<Default><b>She also helped us with
acquiring a new class.</b></Default>

83
00:03:20,629 --> 00:03:23,039
<Default><b>If you want
to help her out</b></Default>

84
00:03:23,129 --> 00:03:25,009
<Default><b>It's not something
I can do!</b></Default>

85
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,240
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

86
00:03:26,379 --> 00:03:29,419
<Default><b>It sounds like it has to be you
and me to help Master.</b></Default>

87
00:03:31,289 --> 00:03:33,249
<Default><b>Are you two
talking right now?</b></Default>

88
00:03:33,289 --> 00:03:34,289
<Default><b>Yep.</b></Default>

89
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:36,580
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

90
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,550
<Default><b>So you're off
to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

91
00:03:38,629 --> 00:03:40,919
<Default><b>[FILO]
{\i1}Um, Master has a question.{\i0}</b></Default>

92
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,186
<Default><b>{\i1}He wants to know if you're going{\i0}
{\i1}to kill off the Cardinal heroes{\i0}</b></Default>

93
00:03:44,210 --> 00:03:47,000
<Default><b>{\i1}if he decides to ignore{\i0}
{\i1}the request you have.{\i0}</b></Default>

94
00:03:48,210 --> 00:03:50,170
<Default><b>I suppose my
request can wait.</b></Default>

95
00:03:50,669 --> 00:03:53,509
<Default><b>But don't blame me if you
end up regretting it later.</b></Default>

96
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,599
<Default><b>[FILO] {\i1}Whatever he says.{\i0}</b></Default>

97
00:04:06,419 --> 00:04:08,039
<Default><b>[♪ Dramatic music]</b></Default>

98
00:04:10,669 --> 00:04:12,189
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Siltvelt.</b></Default>

99
00:04:18,329 --> 00:04:20,629
<Default><b>[♪ Opening music begins]</b></Default>

100
00:04:25,379 --> 00:04:29,170
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

101
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:47,209
<Default><b>[♪ opening music ends]</b></Default>

102
00:05:49,329 --> 00:05:52,579
<Default><b>EPISODE 1: SILTVELT</b></Default>

103
00:05:52,709 --> 00:05:54,459
<Default><b>[♪ tranquil music]</b></Default>

104
00:05:57,629 --> 00:06:00,709
<Default><b>My imitation of the Hangen
Musou Secret Technique.</b></Default>

105
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,790
<Default><b>First dance, sun!</b></Default>

106
00:06:08,829 --> 00:06:10,726
<Default><b>How in the world
is someone like Atla</b></Default>

107
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:12,105
<Default><b>able to fight like that?</b></Default>

108
00:06:12,129 --> 00:06:13,849
<Default><b>That's incredible, Atla!</b></Default>

109
00:06:14,170 --> 00:06:15,976
<Default><b>I guess Claire
was right then.</b></Default>

110
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,516
<Default><b>She really does have a talent
for Hengen Musou.</b></Default>

111
00:06:18,540 --> 00:06:20,660
<Default><b>I have to train harder
from now on.</b></Default>

112
00:06:20,709 --> 00:06:23,909
<Default><b>[WOMEN] The Shield Hero and his
party have returned, everyone!</b></Default>

113
00:06:28,629 --> 00:06:31,726
<Default><b>The plan is for us to reach
the Siltvelt border by tomorrow.</b></Default>

114
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:34,170
<Default><b>Once we're past it</b></Default>

115
00:06:34,290 --> 00:06:36,766
<Default><b>Does that mean I get to pull
the carriage again?</b></Default>

116
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:37,709
<Default><b>Sure does.</b></Default>

117
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:40,805
<Default><b>But we're not going to be able
to take it through the portal.</b></Default>

118
00:06:40,829 --> 00:06:41,896
<Default><b>Hey, Melty.</b></Default>

119
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,226
<Default><b>Can you contact the Queen
and have her prepare</b></Default>

120
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:46,185
<Default><b>a carriage near
the border checkpoint?</b></Default>

121
00:06:46,209 --> 00:06:48,649
<Default><b>You make it sound like
an easy thing to do.</b></Default>

122
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:51,160
<Default><b>I suppose it couldn't hurt
to ask her.</b></Default>

123
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:53,930
<Default><b>Understood. I dare say.</b></Default>

124
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:56,670
<Default><b>So. I know that
Filo's coming.</b></Default>

125
00:06:56,709 --> 00:06:57,726
<Default><b>But who else?</b></Default>

126
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,750
<Default><b>Well, it's a
Demi-human country</b></Default>

127
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:01,959
<Default><b>so taking a royal
like Melty with us</b></Default>

128
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,840
<Default><b>probably
wouldn't be wise.</b></Default>

129
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,600
<Default><b>I'm well aware of that.</b></Default>

130
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,840
<Default><b>Besides, someone has to stay
here and watch your lands.</b></Default>

131
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:10,055
<Default><b>Appreciate it.</b></Default>

132
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:12,119
<Default><b>How about bringing
Fohl and Atla?</b></Default>

133
00:07:13,129 --> 00:07:15,609
<Default><b>The two of them
have been training every day</b></Default>

134
00:07:15,709 --> 00:07:17,949
<Default><b>and pushing each other
to be stronger.</b></Default>

135
00:07:35,250 --> 00:07:37,855
<Default><b>They've come a long way
from when you picked them up</b></Default>

136
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:39,685
<Default><b>in the arena,
haven't they?</b></Default>

137
00:07:39,709 --> 00:07:40,420
<Default><b>No kidding.</b></Default>

138
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:43,579
<Default><b>And their rate of improvement
has been quite unbelievable.</b></Default>

139
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:45,305
<Default><b>Seeing as they're
from Siltvelt</b></Default>

140
00:07:45,329 --> 00:07:47,435
<Default><b>they might be useful
in this scenario.</b></Default>

141
00:07:47,459 --> 00:07:48,379
<Default><b>[REN] Now, for me.</b></Default>

142
00:07:48,459 --> 00:07:49,935
<Default><b>What about
the two of us?</b></Default>

143
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:52,516
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'd love for you
to come along with us</b></Default>

144
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:55,226
<Default><b>but not when your curses
haven't fully healed yet.</b></Default>

145
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:57,185
<Default><b>But they've both gone
out of their way</b></Default>

146
00:07:57,209 --> 00:07:59,055
<Default><b>to bathe in the Carmina
hot springs</b></Default>

147
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:01,055
<Default><b>so shouldn't their curses
be lifted?</b></Default>

148
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,976
<Default><b>Well, the hot springs
are helping</b></Default>

149
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,976
<Default><b>but it's still going
to take some time.</b></Default>

150
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,790
<Default><b>Exactly.</b></Default>

151
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,185
<Default><b>Just focus on recovering</b></Default>

152
00:08:07,209 --> 00:08:09,766
<Default><b>so you're ready to go
when the Phoenix revives.</b></Default>

153
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:10,990
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

154
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:13,555
<Default><b>I'll stay and help with
the recovery process</b></Default>

155
00:08:13,579 --> 00:08:14,939
<Default><b>if that's okay.</b></Default>

156
00:08:15,420 --> 00:08:17,629
<Default><b>So our party
going will be me</b></Default>

157
00:08:17,709 --> 00:08:18,805
<Default><b>Raphtalia</b></Default>

158
00:08:18,829 --> 00:08:19,829
<Default><b>Filo</b></Default>

159
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:22,209
<Default><b>Sadeena, Fohl, and Atla.</b></Default>

160
00:08:22,329 --> 00:08:23,489
<Default><b>[RAPH] Ra…</b></Default>

161
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:26,000
<Default><b>And of course,
you too, Raffy.</b></Default>

162
00:08:26,129 --> 00:08:27,129
<Default><b>Raffy.</b></Default>

163
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,629
<Default><b>So</b></Default>

164
00:08:28,709 --> 00:08:31,579
<Default><b>did any Q'ten Lo assassins
attack while I was away?</b></Default>

165
00:08:31,670 --> 00:08:33,556
<Default><b>It's actually been
rather quiet here.</b></Default>

166
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:35,645
<Default><b>There hasn't been
any sign of them since</b></Default>

167
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:37,105
<Default><b>that first attack
happened.</b></Default>

168
00:08:37,129 --> 00:08:37,629
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

169
00:08:37,710 --> 00:08:39,039
<Default><b>The people...</b></Default>

170
00:08:39,129 --> 00:08:40,855
<Default><b>The people from
my master's world</b></Default>

171
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:42,556
<Default><b>should be after
this village too</b></Default>

172
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:45,556
<Default><b>but there is no sign of them
either. Think what you want.</b></Default>

173
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,265
<Default><b>What the hell is
going on here?</b></Default>

174
00:08:47,289 --> 00:08:50,265
<Default><b>Are they being cautious since
their scouts were eliminated?</b></Default>

175
00:08:50,289 --> 00:08:52,105
<Default><b>I hope that's
what this means.</b></Default>

176
00:08:52,129 --> 00:08:54,689
<Default><b>I was looking forward
to helping fend them off</b></Default>

177
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,806
<Default><b>but things here
have been peaceful.</b></Default>

178
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:59,186
<Default><b>I guess I'll have to be useful
in other ways.</b></Default>

179
00:08:59,210 --> 00:09:01,515
<Default><b>We just have to be ready
when they attack.</b></Default>

180
00:09:01,539 --> 00:09:02,895
<Default><b>Um, by the way.</b></Default>

181
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,726
<Default><b>Does anyone know
where Motoyasu</b></Default>

182
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:06,686
<Default><b>could be or what
he might be doing?</b></Default>

183
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:07,936
<Default><b>As weird as he is</b></Default>

184
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,015
<Default><b>he'd be useful to have
here right now.</b></Default>

185
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:11,159
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

186
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:14,306
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU] You
have some nerve</b></Default>

187
00:09:14,330 --> 00:09:16,730
<Default><b>thinking you can invade
my father's lands.</b></Default>

188
00:09:17,210 --> 00:09:18,855
<Default><b>You're not
the first, either.</b></Default>

189
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:21,799
<Default><b>There were also some dudes
dressed like ninjas earlier.</b></Default>

190
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,710
<Default><b>For my father and</b></Default>

191
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:26,330
<Default><b>for my beloved Filo</b></Default>

192
00:09:26,419 --> 00:09:29,500
<Default><b>I will destroy you
and obliterate your souls.</b></Default>

193
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:30,210
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

194
00:09:30,289 --> 00:09:31,000
<Default><b>Please stop.</b></Default>

195
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:33,476
<Default><b>I don't want to die
at the hands of some weirdo.</b></Default>

196
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,780
<Default><b>Bye, bye now.</b></Default>

197
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:36,610
<Default><b>[♪ Heroic music]</b></Default>

198
00:09:37,330 --> 00:09:38,500
<Default><b>Onward!</b></Default>

199
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:41,629
<Default><b>The next group of evil doers
demands my retribution.</b></Default>

200
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:43,210
<Default><b>[evil laugh]</b></Default>

201
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:52,460
<Default><b>Well, how do you like
the carriage, Filo?</b></Default>

202
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:54,940
<Default><b>It feels like they used
a different wood.</b></Default>

203
00:09:55,289 --> 00:09:57,809
<Default><b>Does it really make that big
of a difference?</b></Default>

204
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:58,789
<Default><b>Mmm…</b></Default>

205
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:00,395
<Default><b>Maybe a little bit.</b></Default>

206
00:10:00,419 --> 00:10:02,145
<Default><b>Not sure what
that means.</b></Default>

207
00:10:02,169 --> 00:10:03,645
<Default><b>[GIRL] It's the
shield hero!</b></Default>

208
00:10:03,669 --> 00:10:06,395
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Looks like a
crowd starting to gather here.</b></Default>

209
00:10:06,419 --> 00:10:09,605
<Default><b>I'm guessing that when the Queen
arranged this carriage for us</b></Default>

210
00:10:09,629 --> 00:10:12,515
<Default><b>rumor must have spread through
town that we were coming.</b></Default>

211
00:10:12,539 --> 00:10:14,765
<Default><b>Make sure to stay
on your guard, everyone.</b></Default>

212
00:10:14,789 --> 00:10:15,379
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

213
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:17,145
<Default><b>Why don't we
take a break?</b></Default>

214
00:10:17,169 --> 00:10:18,039
<Default><b>I think all of us</b></Default>

215
00:10:18,129 --> 00:10:20,729
<Default><b>would be in better spirits
with a little drink.</b></Default>

216
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:31,580
<Default><b>Pardon me, Your Majesty</b></Default>

217
00:10:32,169 --> 00:10:34,105
<Default><b>The false Empress
and her companions</b></Default>

218
00:10:34,129 --> 00:10:36,015
<Default><b>have just
arrived in Siltvelt.</b></Default>

219
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:38,639
<Default><b>I understand that this news
might be worrisome.</b></Default>

220
00:10:40,379 --> 00:10:42,765
<Default><b>But I assure you, I'll take
care of everything.</b></Default>

221
00:10:42,789 --> 00:10:45,710
<Default><b>I shall cut down the Shield Hero
and this traitor</b></Default>

222
00:10:45,789 --> 00:10:47,726
<Default><b>who seeks to rob you
of your throne.</b></Default>

223
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,190
<Default><b>You have my word.</b></Default>

224
00:10:49,250 --> 00:10:51,556
<Default><b>The two of them won't live
to see Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

225
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:54,789
<Default><b>You put your trust in me</b></Default>

226
00:10:54,879 --> 00:10:56,169
<Default><b>[thunder]</b></Default>

227
00:10:56,669 --> 00:10:57,909
<Default><b>[evil smirk]</b></Default>

228
00:10:59,789 --> 00:11:01,250
<Default><b>[♪ Joyful music]</b></Default>

229
00:11:01,330 --> 00:11:03,056
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What do you think, Fohl?</b></Default>

230
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,600
<Default><b>Feel like home yet?</b></Default>

231
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:05,976
<Default><b>Not exactly.</b></Default>

232
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,355
<Default><b>I've never been to this part
of the country.</b></Default>

233
00:11:08,379 --> 00:11:10,899
<Default><b>I don't remember being here
very much either.</b></Default>

234
00:11:12,129 --> 00:11:13,686
<Default><b>Something
isn't right here.</b></Default>

235
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:16,390
<Default><b>We made it through
the checkpoint way too easily.</b></Default>

236
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:18,630
<Default><b>Wonder what
that's all about?</b></Default>

237
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,855
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
What does that banner say?</b></Default>

238
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:22,976
<Default><b>Can anyone read that?</b></Default>

239
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,436
<Default><b>[SADEENA] You don't need to know
how to read it.</b></Default>

240
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:27,355
<Default><b>Just look around
at everyone's faces.</b></Default>

241
00:11:27,379 --> 00:11:28,806
<Default><b>[FOHL] Oh,
that big banner.</b></Default>

242
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:31,789
<Default><b>It looks like someone's written
welcome Shield Hero.</b></Default>

243
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,789
<Default><b>Oh, interesting.</b></Default>

244
00:11:34,169 --> 00:11:35,355
<Default><b>So you can read it?</b></Default>

245
00:11:35,379 --> 00:11:37,265
<Default><b>Being able to read
stuff like that</b></Default>

246
00:11:37,289 --> 00:11:39,436
<Default><b>is the one useful skill
my brother has.</b></Default>

247
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:40,250
<Default><b>Not true.</b></Default>

248
00:11:40,330 --> 00:11:41,410
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

249
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,720
<Default><b>Just keep going, Filo.</b></Default>

250
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:52,830
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

251
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,726
<Default><b>[GUARD] If you
don't mind, sir.</b></Default>

252
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:58,250
<Default><b>The Royal Guard would be
honored to escort</b></Default>

253
00:11:58,330 --> 00:12:00,960
<Default><b>the Shield Hero and his party
to the palace.</b></Default>

254
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:02,199
<Default><b>Follow me!</b></Default>

255
00:12:02,539 --> 00:12:04,259
<Default><b>[cheering and galloping]</b></Default>

256
00:12:05,629 --> 00:12:08,750
<Default><b>Even though I expect to see this
kind of thing from Siltvelt</b></Default>

257
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:11,750
<Default><b>it's nice to see them treating
Master Naofumi this way.</b></Default>

258
00:12:11,789 --> 00:12:13,806
<Default><b>He deserves this
kind of treatment.</b></Default>

259
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:15,030
<Default><b>Easy there.</b></Default>

260
00:12:16,250 --> 00:12:19,370
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I feel like I'm the
star of a parade or something.</b></Default>

261
00:12:20,129 --> 00:12:23,080
<Default><b>Even I'm surprised to see
a turnout for you like this.</b></Default>

262
00:12:23,669 --> 00:12:26,000
<Default><b>You've become quite
a revered hero, huh?</b></Default>

263
00:12:26,250 --> 00:12:27,726
<Default><b>You know, I
just remembered</b></Default>

264
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:30,645
<Default><b>what the Queen of Melromarc
once told me about Siltvelt.</b></Default>

265
00:12:30,669 --> 00:12:31,289
<Default><b>Oh dear.</b></Default>

266
00:12:31,379 --> 00:12:33,419
<Default><b>What did she
say about Siltvelt?</b></Default>

267
00:12:33,669 --> 00:12:34,829
<Default><b>First off…</b></Default>

268
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:35,919
<Default><b>{\i1}First off</b></Default>

269
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,476
<Default><b>{\i1}You're going
to be welcomed{\i0}</b></Default>

270
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:39,919
<Default><b>{\i1}and then approached{\i0}
{\i1}by noble women.{\i0}</b></Default>

271
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:43,160
<Default><b>{\i1}After that, they'll attempt to{\i0}
{\i1}form a type of harem for you{\i0}</b></Default>

272
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,879
<Default><b>{\i1}with women from any{\i0}
{\i1}number of species.{\i0}</b></Default>

273
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:47,910
<Default><b>{\i1}A harem?{\i0}</b></Default>

274
00:12:48,210 --> 00:12:49,879
<Default><b>{\i1}After that</b></Default>

275
00:12:49,919 --> 00:12:52,080
<Default><b>{\i1}fall victim to{\i0}
{\i1}an unknown disease.{\i0}</b></Default>

276
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:54,710
<Default><b>{\i1}And once it becomes{\i0}
{\i1}too much, you'll…{\i0}</b></Default>

277
00:12:55,210 --> 00:12:55,789
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

278
00:12:55,879 --> 00:12:57,726
<Default><b>Something like that
is impossible.</b></Default>

279
00:12:57,750 --> 00:12:59,306
<Default><b>If it isn't
obvious already</b></Default>

280
00:12:59,330 --> 00:13:02,580
<Default><b>the people of Siltvelt worship
the Shield Hero as a god.</b></Default>

281
00:13:02,669 --> 00:13:04,605
<Default><b>I would never do something
like that.</b></Default>

282
00:13:04,629 --> 00:13:06,556
<Default><b>Yeah, well, I sure hope
you're right.</b></Default>

283
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:07,629
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

284
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:11,265
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Well, either way</b></Default>

285
00:13:11,289 --> 00:13:13,476
<Default><b>we need to try and get
through this country</b></Default>

286
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:15,180
<Default><b>as quickly as possible.</b></Default>

287
00:13:21,330 --> 00:13:24,330
<Default><b>[♪ Soft music]</b></Default>

288
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:33,100
<Default><b>[MAN] It's a pleasure to
meet you, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

289
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:33,960
<Default><b>Welcome.</b></Default>

290
00:13:34,289 --> 00:13:37,419
<Default><b>On behalf of Siltvelt</b></Default>

291
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:39,799
<Default><b>Allow me to
introduce myself.</b></Default>

292
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:44,629
<Default><b>My name is Werner</b></Default>

293
00:13:44,710 --> 00:13:46,910
<Default><b>of the Shusaku race
here in Siltvelt.</b></Default>

294
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:49,379
<Default><b>I'm happy to help
however I can.</b></Default>

295
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:50,580
<Default><b>{\i1}Shusaku?{\i0}</b></Default>

296
00:13:50,669 --> 00:13:53,210
<Default><b>Well, then, my name is
Naofumi Iwatani.</b></Default>

297
00:13:54,039 --> 00:13:54,789
<Default><b>And this is.</b></Default>

298
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,419
<Default><b>I am Raphtalia</b></Default>

299
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,379
<Default><b>Oh, and my name's Filo.
Nice to meet you.</b></Default>

300
00:14:00,539 --> 00:14:01,580
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

301
00:14:01,830 --> 00:14:03,056
<Default><b>My name's Sadeena.</b></Default>

302
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,539
<Default><b>My name is Atla.</b></Default>

303
00:14:04,629 --> 00:14:05,909
<Default><b>And I'm Fohl.</b></Default>

304
00:14:06,539 --> 00:14:08,395
<Default><b>Know that you are
all welcome here.</b></Default>

305
00:14:08,419 --> 00:14:09,726
<Default><b>Believe it or not</b></Default>

306
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:13,000
<Default><b>I purchased those two back when
they were slaves in Zeltoble.</b></Default>

307
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:15,530
<Default><b>But they're not pure
blood Demi humans.</b></Default>

308
00:14:15,629 --> 00:14:18,436
<Default><b>I don't plan on getting involved
in any power struggles</b></Default>

309
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:20,976
<Default><b>in your country, or letting
them get involved.</b></Default>

310
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,960
<Default><b>I appreciate
your reassurance.</b></Default>

311
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:25,720
<Default><b>Please, I'd like you to join me
inside the palace.</b></Default>

312
00:14:27,710 --> 00:14:30,436
<Default><b>I'm sure you must be exhausted
from your long journey</b></Default>

313
00:14:30,460 --> 00:14:31,169
<Default><b>Shield Hero</b></Default>

314
00:14:31,250 --> 00:14:33,145
<Default><b>but if you wouldn't
mind me doing so</b></Default>

315
00:14:33,169 --> 00:14:35,750
<Default><b>I'd like to request
an audience.</b></Default>

316
00:14:36,129 --> 00:14:37,369
<Default><b>An audience?</b></Default>

317
00:14:37,629 --> 00:14:39,229
<Default><b>Between who, exactly?</b></Default>

318
00:14:53,039 --> 00:14:54,056
<Default><b>[WERNER] I'm afraid</b></Default>

319
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:56,600
<Default><b>your servants
aren't allowed past this point.</b></Default>

320
00:15:18,919 --> 00:15:20,645
<Default><b>[WERNER]
As you see, Shield Hero</b></Default>

321
00:15:20,669 --> 00:15:23,580
<Default><b>the races that have ruled
over Siltvelt until now</b></Default>

322
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:26,210
<Default><b>have gathered here
before you in order to</b></Default>

323
00:15:26,289 --> 00:15:28,409
<Default><b>properly welcome you
into our city.</b></Default>

324
00:15:29,289 --> 00:15:32,080
<Default><b>I'm Solea of the Genmu race.
Honored to meet you.</b></Default>

325
00:15:32,879 --> 00:15:34,629
<Default><b>And my name is Tsualon.</b></Default>

326
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:37,789
<Default><b>I represent the Aotatsu.
It is a privilege to meet you.</b></Default>

327
00:15:40,669 --> 00:15:41,669
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

328
00:15:42,379 --> 00:15:44,460
<Default><b>Thank you for
that, I guess.</b></Default>

329
00:15:45,539 --> 00:15:47,099
<Default><b>Your words honor me.</b></Default>

330
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:50,260
<Default><b>So is this how an audience
is supposed to work here?</b></Default>

331
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:50,919
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

332
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:54,120
<Default><b>You must understand we're
overwhelmed with joy to see you.</b></Default>

333
00:15:54,669 --> 00:15:56,265
<Default><b>Then… I'll just come out</b></Default>

334
00:15:56,289 --> 00:15:58,645
<Default><b>and say exactly what I need
from you all.</b></Default>

335
00:15:58,669 --> 00:15:59,789
<Default><b>Yes, Sir.</b></Default>

336
00:16:01,789 --> 00:16:04,509
<Default><b>I don't have any interest
in taking over Siltvelt.</b></Default>

337
00:16:04,539 --> 00:16:06,299
<Default><b>So rest easy
knowing that</b></Default>

338
00:16:06,879 --> 00:16:09,830
<Default><b>I'm merely passing through
on my way to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

339
00:16:10,419 --> 00:16:12,265
<Default><b>I don't intend on getting
in the way</b></Default>

340
00:16:12,289 --> 00:16:13,806
<Default><b>of how you
do things here</b></Default>

341
00:16:13,830 --> 00:16:15,750
<Default><b>or how you
rule this country.</b></Default>

342
00:16:16,129 --> 00:16:17,186
<Default><b>On that note</b></Default>

343
00:16:17,210 --> 00:16:19,895
<Default><b>I'd like you to prepare
a ship to Q'ten Lo for me.</b></Default>

344
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:22,039
<Default><b>And as soon as possible</b></Default>

345
00:16:23,330 --> 00:16:24,395
<Default><b>I see now.</b></Default>

346
00:16:24,419 --> 00:16:26,015
<Default><b>You seem to be
misunderstanding</b></Default>

347
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:27,919
<Default><b>the situation before you</b></Default>

348
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:29,540
<Default><b>How so?</b></Default>

349
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:32,726
<Default><b>First, I would like you to rest
from your long journey here.</b></Default>

350
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,476
<Default><b>After you've gotten
enough rest</b></Default>

351
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:36,355
<Default><b>and participate
in tonight's banquet</b></Default>

352
00:16:36,379 --> 00:16:38,765
<Default><b>we'd be more than happy
to hear any requests</b></Default>

353
00:16:38,789 --> 00:16:40,226
<Default><b>that you might
have for us.</b></Default>

354
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:42,056
<Default><b>I don't have time
for any of that.</b></Default>

355
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:45,306
<Default><b>And I'm sure it's safe to assume
some of you want me out of here</b></Default>

356
00:16:45,330 --> 00:16:46,726
<Default><b>as soon as
possible, right?</b></Default>

357
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,145
<Default><b>[WERNER] I
can't deny that.</b></Default>

358
00:16:48,169 --> 00:16:50,936
<Default><b>But please know we don't share
in that way of thinking.</b></Default>

359
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:53,840
<Default><b>That is a sickness in our
country that must be purged.</b></Default>

360
00:16:54,039 --> 00:16:56,265
<Default><b>Anyone who doesn't want
Master Naofumi here</b></Default>

361
00:16:56,289 --> 00:16:58,169
<Default><b>is a traitor to
his country.</b></Default>

362
00:16:58,210 --> 00:17:01,210
<Default><b>We should round them up
and execute them all.</b></Default>

363
00:17:02,669 --> 00:17:04,726
<Default><b>While your name evokes
discourse in some</b></Default>

364
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:08,039
<Default><b>please know our undying loyalty
to you remains unaltered.</b></Default>

365
00:17:08,289 --> 00:17:10,569
<Default><b>It's important to us
you remember that.</b></Default>

366
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,396
<Default><b>What a pleasant thought</b></Default>

367
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:15,079
<Default><b>to swear my loyalty
to Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

368
00:17:15,170 --> 00:17:16,436
<Default><b>If you're loyal, then</b></Default>

369
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:19,515
<Default><b>shouldn't you be trying to grant
my wish as soon as possible?</b></Default>

370
00:17:19,539 --> 00:17:22,106
<Default><b>We'd be more than happy
to prepare a ship for you.</b></Default>

371
00:17:22,130 --> 00:17:23,265
<Default><b>But please.</b></Default>

372
00:17:23,289 --> 00:17:25,515
<Default><b>You must understand
that we'd be heartbroken</b></Default>

373
00:17:25,539 --> 00:17:28,000
<Default><b>if the God we worship
left in a hurry.</b></Default>

374
00:17:28,079 --> 00:17:30,759
<Default><b>I mean, after all, you've only
just arrived here.</b></Default>

375
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:33,680
<Default><b>Is this country really just
a stop on your journey?</b></Default>

376
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:36,976
<Default><b>You saw how the people in the
streets worshipped you, right?</b></Default>

377
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,106
<Default><b>If you were to leave us
so suddenly</b></Default>

378
00:17:39,130 --> 00:17:41,896
<Default><b>our city and all of its people
would be left thinking</b></Default>

379
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:45,160
<Default><b>that you abandoned Siltvelt. Is
that really something you want?</b></Default>

380
00:17:45,789 --> 00:17:47,976
<Default><b>Of course not. But I don't
have time for...</b></Default>

381
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,789
<Default><b>I'd go so far as to say there
may even be riots</b></Default>

382
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,280
<Default><b>and a military {\i1}coup{\i0}
{\i1}d'état{\i0} if you left us.</b></Default>

383
00:17:53,829 --> 00:17:55,646
<Default><b>I hope that helps you
to understand</b></Default>

384
00:17:55,670 --> 00:17:58,289
<Default><b>just how much you mean
to this nation of ours.</b></Default>

385
00:17:58,380 --> 00:18:00,630
<Default><b>So please, I beg you</b></Default>

386
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:03,710
<Default><b>please be the Shield Hero that
all of us have waited for.</b></Default>

387
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,289
<Default><b>All right, fine.</b></Default>

388
00:18:13,380 --> 00:18:16,540
<Default><b>I will attend this banquet of
yours, if that's what you want.</b></Default>

389
00:18:17,670 --> 00:18:18,289
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

390
00:18:18,460 --> 00:18:21,555
<Default><b>You'll be delighted to know that
we've planned a room for you</b></Default>

391
00:18:21,579 --> 00:18:23,936
<Default><b>and a room for each one
of your followers.</b></Default>

392
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:27,120
<Default><b>We ask that you please remain
there until the banquet begins.</b></Default>

393
00:18:27,579 --> 00:18:29,920
<Default><b>I don't want us
in separate rooms.</b></Default>

394
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,920
<Default><b>{\i1}I can't imagine{\i0}</b></Default>

395
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,436
<Default><b>{\i1}they'll try anything on me{\i0}
{\i1}at this very moment</b></Default>

396
00:18:33,460 --> 00:18:35,976
<Default><b>{\i1}but I don't want to be alone{\i0}
{\i1}just in case they do.{\i0}</b></Default>

397
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,646
<Default><b>I understand
your concern, sir.</b></Default>

398
00:18:37,670 --> 00:18:39,936
<Default><b>But we cannot treat others
in the same manner</b></Default>

399
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,765
<Default><b>we would treat
the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

400
00:18:41,789 --> 00:18:45,079
<Default><b>Doing so would be a mockery
to the faith we believe in.</b></Default>

401
00:18:45,630 --> 00:18:46,790
<Default><b>[ATLA] Um…</b></Default>

402
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:50,710
<Default><b>If it isn't too
much trouble</b></Default>

403
00:18:50,789 --> 00:18:52,976
<Default><b>a room next to Master
Naofumi for me?</b></Default>

404
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:55,356
<Default><b>Who gave that white tiger
permission to talk?</b></Default>

405
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:57,380
<Default><b>What an absurd
request to make.</b></Default>

406
00:19:02,789 --> 00:19:04,476
<Default><b>[WERNER] Very
well, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

407
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:06,580
<Default><b>I'll have it prepared
immediately.</b></Default>

408
00:19:07,130 --> 00:19:09,476
<Default><b>While there's still time
before the banquet</b></Default>

409
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,265
<Default><b>I'd much rather go out
and explore</b></Default>

410
00:19:11,289 --> 00:19:13,849
<Default><b>the town than stay cooped up
inside of a room.</b></Default>

411
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:16,515
<Default><b>The people of Siltvelt would be
honored to see you.</b></Default>

412
00:19:16,539 --> 00:19:17,765
<Default><b>How wonderful.</b></Default>

413
00:19:17,789 --> 00:19:19,396
<Default><b>Okay, then.
Let's get going.</b></Default>

414
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:20,820
<Default><b>[WERNER] However</b></Default>

415
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:23,015
<Default><b>I'm afraid it will take
some time to make</b></Default>

416
00:19:23,039 --> 00:19:25,630
<Default><b>the necessary arrangements
for a royal visit.</b></Default>

417
00:19:26,250 --> 00:19:27,856
<Default><b>Understand,
a sudden visit</b></Default>

418
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:30,789
<Default><b>from the Shield Hero might
catch people off guard.</b></Default>

419
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:32,146
<Default><b>If that happened</b></Default>

420
00:19:32,170 --> 00:19:34,810
<Default><b>they'd regret not offering
you a proper welcome.</b></Default>

421
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:38,170
<Default><b>Such a major event requires
preparations to be made.</b></Default>

422
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:40,976
<Default><b>The people must be told in
advance of your arrival.</b></Default>

423
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:43,856
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] All right, fine.
I'll stay inside the palace.</b></Default>

424
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:46,360
<Default><b>Am I at least allowed to walk
around inside?</b></Default>

425
00:19:46,579 --> 00:19:48,015
<Default><b>Why, of course you are.</b></Default>

426
00:19:48,039 --> 00:19:51,079
<Default><b>I mean, after all, this is
your palace we're in.</b></Default>

427
00:19:52,079 --> 00:19:53,646
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yet
I'm on a leash.</b></Default>

428
00:19:53,670 --> 00:19:55,646
<Default><b>And I'm not allowed in
any of the rooms</b></Default>

429
00:19:55,670 --> 00:19:57,510
<Default><b>as they're
being renovated.</b></Default>

430
00:19:57,539 --> 00:19:59,829
<Default><b>So much for this
being my palace.</b></Default>

431
00:20:01,039 --> 00:20:02,555
<Default><b>You gotta be kidding me.</b></Default>

432
00:20:02,579 --> 00:20:05,329
<Default><b>How many days are we gonna
waste in this place?</b></Default>

433
00:20:06,579 --> 00:20:08,186
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Seeing how that went</b></Default>

434
00:20:08,210 --> 00:20:10,930
<Default><b>we'd be lucky if we weren't
stuck here for months.</b></Default>

435
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:11,789
<Default><b>If that happens</b></Default>

436
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:14,356
<Default><b>we won't have time to get ready
for the Phoenix.</b></Default>

437
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,130
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

438
00:20:15,210 --> 00:20:16,356
<Default><b>I guess you're right.</b></Default>

439
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:18,726
<Default><b>I respect their loyalty
to Master Naofumi</b></Default>

440
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:20,436
<Default><b>but they're too
strict with him.</b></Default>

441
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:23,130
<Default><b>If they really
do worship him</b></Default>

442
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,420
<Default><b>This must be how
the other heroes felt</b></Default>

443
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:28,896
<Default><b>when they were worshipped
as gods in Melromarc.</b></Default>

444
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:30,710
<Default><b>But even if that's true</b></Default>

445
00:20:30,789 --> 00:20:32,606
<Default><b>they certainly
didn't act the same.</b></Default>

446
00:20:32,630 --> 00:20:34,856
<Default><b>They were a lot more free
spirited than you.</b></Default>

447
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:37,055
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
I don't know, you'd have to be a</b></Default>

448
00:20:37,079 --> 00:20:39,555
<Default><b>pretty free spirit to ask them
to give you a ship</b></Default>

449
00:20:39,579 --> 00:20:42,356
<Default><b>without first serving your duty
to them as Shield Hero</b></Default>

450
00:20:42,380 --> 00:20:43,250
<Default><b>wouldn't you say?</b></Default>

451
00:20:43,329 --> 00:20:45,436
<Default><b>I can't believe you
were able to say that</b></Default>

452
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:46,976
<Default><b>to them with
a straight face.</b></Default>

453
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,805
<Default><b>Look, I know it sounded
a bit harsh</b></Default>

454
00:20:48,829 --> 00:20:51,686
<Default><b>but we don't have the time
to waste parading around here.</b></Default>

455
00:20:51,710 --> 00:20:53,515
<Default><b>Cut him some slack.
The only reason</b></Default>

456
00:20:53,539 --> 00:20:56,015
<Default><b>Master Naofumi is hurrying
things along like this</b></Default>

457
00:20:56,039 --> 00:20:57,896
<Default><b>is cause he wants
to help Raphtalia.</b></Default>

458
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:59,856
<Default><b>I know, you don't have
to tell me.</b></Default>

459
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:01,015
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] I'm sorry.</b></Default>

460
00:21:01,039 --> 00:21:03,106
<Default><b>I feel like I've caused
everyone trouble.</b></Default>

461
00:21:03,130 --> 00:21:05,226
<Default><b>[ATLA] Has something
like this happened</b></Default>

462
00:21:05,250 --> 00:21:07,880
<Default><b>you would do
the same for me</b></Default>

463
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,805
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Where did that come from?</b></Default>

464
00:21:09,829 --> 00:21:12,309
<Default><b>[MAN] Well now.
If it isn't the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

465
00:21:12,789 --> 00:21:14,229
<Default><b>Who might you be?</b></Default>

466
00:21:15,079 --> 00:21:16,896
<Default><b>My name is
Jaralis, and I serve</b></Default>

467
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:19,460
<Default><b>as the representative
of the Lyle race.</b></Default>

468
00:21:19,539 --> 00:21:21,939
<Default><b>It's a pleasure
to make your acquaintance.</b></Default>

469
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:23,579
<Default><b>{\i1}A lion Demi-human?{\i0}</b></Default>

470
00:21:24,079 --> 00:21:26,555
<Default><b>I hope you're able to forgive me
for only now</b></Default>

471
00:21:26,579 --> 00:21:29,630
<Default><b>being able to come down here
and introduce myself to you.</b></Default>

472
00:21:29,789 --> 00:21:31,305
<Default><b>No need to mention it.</b></Default>

473
00:21:31,329 --> 00:21:33,039
<Default><b>Allow me to be frank</b></Default>

474
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:35,606
<Default><b>Most of us caught wind
of what you mentioned</b></Default>

475
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:37,936
<Default><b>during your audience
earlier with Werner.</b></Default>

476
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:40,396
<Default><b>If you wish to have a ship
arranged to Q'ten Lo</b></Default>

477
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:43,015
<Default><b>please know I'm able and willing
to do such a thing</b></Default>

478
00:21:43,039 --> 00:21:45,199
<Default><b>for you, if that is
what you desire.</b></Default>

479
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:48,476
<Default><b>I find it troubling you weren't
present at the audience earlier.</b></Default>

480
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:51,436
<Default><b>I have a hard time believing
that someone who wasn't there</b></Default>

481
00:21:51,460 --> 00:21:53,500
<Default><b>would be capable
of such a thing.</b></Default>

482
00:21:53,789 --> 00:21:55,686
<Default><b>Very well, then.
I will look forward</b></Default>

483
00:21:55,710 --> 00:21:58,350
<Default><b>to seeing you at
tonight's banquet, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

484
00:21:58,380 --> 00:22:00,860
<Default><b>I apologize if I've troubled you
in any way.</b></Default>

485
00:22:11,420 --> 00:22:14,329
<Default><b>Wow, we're so high up.</b></Default>

486
00:22:18,210 --> 00:22:19,079
<Default><b>Hey, Fohl</b></Default>

487
00:22:19,170 --> 00:22:21,930
<Default><b>do you know anything about
that Jaralis guy we met?</b></Default>

488
00:22:22,460 --> 00:22:23,700
<Default><b>Nope. Sorry.</b></Default>

489
00:22:24,250 --> 00:22:26,850
<Default><b>It's my first time seeing
this Werner guy, too.</b></Default>

490
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:29,480
<Default><b>I did warn you all he's good
for his reading.</b></Default>

491
00:22:29,539 --> 00:22:30,539
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

492
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:33,240
<Default><b>Honestly, I don't trust
either of them.</b></Default>

493
00:22:33,460 --> 00:22:36,250
<Default><b>But if Jarlus is willing
to prepare a ship for us</b></Default>

494
00:22:36,329 --> 00:22:38,106
<Default><b>I think it's pretty safe
to assume</b></Default>

495
00:22:38,130 --> 00:22:40,646
<Default><b>he's probably not
on the same side as Werner.</b></Default>

496
00:22:40,670 --> 00:22:43,356
<Default><b>He may not be important enough
to serve an audience</b></Default>

497
00:22:43,380 --> 00:22:45,936
<Default><b>but I get the feeling that
he does have some power.</b></Default>

498
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:48,320
<Default><b>So we should probably
keep an eye on him.</b></Default>

499
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:50,900
<Default><b>That's my impression. But what
do you think?</b></Default>

500
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:54,160
<Default><b>Well, there's no telling when
we'll be able to leave Siltvelt</b></Default>

501
00:22:54,210 --> 00:22:57,370
<Default><b>if we continue letting the bird
guy boss us around like this.</b></Default>

502
00:22:57,500 --> 00:23:00,340
<Default><b>But the lion's offer almost
seems too good to be true</b></Default>

503
00:23:00,380 --> 00:23:01,039
<Default><b>doesn't it?</b></Default>

504
00:23:01,130 --> 00:23:03,805
<Default><b>If we were to side with one
of them, I have a feeling</b></Default>

505
00:23:03,829 --> 00:23:06,436
<Default><b>it would lead to making
an enemy out of the other.</b></Default>

506
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:09,540
<Default><b>Well, in that case I guess we'll
just have to wait and see.</b></Default>

507
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:13,329
<Default><b>This is all too
complicated for me.</b></Default>

508
00:23:13,420 --> 00:23:15,146
<Default><b>I'm hungry. When
are we eating?</b></Default>

509
00:23:15,170 --> 00:23:16,810
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Soon enough.</b></Default>

510
00:23:27,130 --> 00:23:30,710
<Default><b>Q'ten Lo is a
long way off</b></Default>

511
00:23:36,250 --> 00:23:39,250
<Default><b>OFFICIAL WELCOME</b></Default>

